tion's%20policies%20while%20Trump%20keeps%20firm%20his%20stance%20on%20rapid%20military%20action.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3ENevada%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnNevada%2C%20traditionally%20a%20Democratic%20stronghold%2C%20shows%20signs%20of%20a%20tightening%20race%2C%20with%20recent%20polls%20suggesting%20a%20shift%20in%20favour%20of%20Republicans.%20Both%20campaigns%20are%20actively%20courting%20Nevada's%20substantial%20Latino%20population%2C%20crucial%20to%20any%20candidate's%20success%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20economic%20recovery%20post-COVID%20has%20been%20sluggish%20in%20Nevada%20compared%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%2C%20making%20it%20a%20big%20concern.%20The%20high%20unemployment%20rate%20and%20cost-of-living%20pressures%20are%20also%20key%20issues%20for%20voters%20in%20this%20state.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3ENorth%20Carolina%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20North%20Carolina%2C%20Donald%20Trump's%20narrow%20victory%20margin%20in%202020%20(by%2074%2C000%20votes)%20has%20made%20this%20state%20a%20toss-up%20for%202024.%20With%20demographics%20and%20issues%20mirroring%20those%20of%20neighbouring%20Georgia%20and%20Arizona%2C%20both%20candidates%20are%20pouring%20resources%20into%20North%20Carolina.%20Trump%20recently%20held%20a%20rally%20here%2C%20promising%20to%20end%20inflation%2C%20stop%20the%20influx%20of%20criminals%20into%20the%20country%20and%20restore%20the%20American%20dream.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EPennsylvania%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnPennsylvania%20holds%2019%20electoral%20votes%20and%20is%20a%20critical%20target%20for%20both%20candidates.%20Biden's%20roots%20in%20Scranton%20give%20him%20a%20personal%20connection%20to%20voters%20in%20this%20working-class%20state.%20The%20economic%20landscape%20has%20shifted%20dramatically%20since%20Biden%20took%20office%2C%20with%20inflation%20affecting%20household%20budgets.%20Recent%20statistics%20show%20that%20grocery%20prices%20in%20Pennsylvania%20have%20risen%20faster%20than%20in%20any%20other%20state%2C%20leading%20to%20significant%20cost-of-living%20pressures%20among%20residents.%20Both%20campaigns%20are%20acutely%20aware%20that%20economic%20issues%20could%20sway%20undecided%20voters%2C%20particularly%20in%20counties%20like%20Erie%2C%20where%20food%20insecurity%20is%20a%20growing%20concern.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EWisconsin%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnFinally%2C%20Wisconsin%20has%20historically%20been%20a%20bellwether%20state%2C%20having%20backed%20the%20winning%20candidate%20in%20the%20last%20two%20elections.%20After%20a%20victory%20with%20just%20over%2021%2C000%20votes%20for%20Biden%20in%202020%2C%20the%20state%20is%20crucial%20for%20both%20the%20candidates.%20There%20is%20a%20growing%20concern%20about%20third-party%20candidates%20potentially%20syphoning%20votes%20away%20from%20the%20main%20candidates.%20Independent%20candidate%20Robert%20F%20Kennedy%20Jr%20suspended%20his%20campaign%20in%20late%20August%20and%20endorsed%20Trump%2C%20which%20could%20alter%20the%20dynamics%20in%20this%20tightly%20contested%20state.%20Democrats%20are%20also%20facing%20challenges%20with%20Green%20Party%20candidate%20Jill%20Stein%2C%20whose%20inclusion%20on%20the%20ballot%20has%20been%20contested.%20Trump%20has%20stressed%20Wisconsin's%20significance%2C%20declaring%20that%20winning%20the%20state%20could%20clinch%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730359920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Foh3m2dlg_donald-trump-kamala-harris_625x300_31_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fthe-seven-swing-states-that-could-shape-the-2024-presidential-race-6913487%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20year%2C%20seven%20states%20are%20in%20the%20spotlight%20Arizona%2C%20Georgia%2C%20Michigan%2C%20Nevada%2C%20North%20Carolina%2C%20Pennsylvania%20and%20Wisconsin.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fthe-seven-swing-states-that-could-shape-the-2024-presidential-race-6913487%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BSome%20Perverted%20Powers...%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20Modi's%20Strong%20Message%20From%20Statue%20Of%20Unity%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETargeting%20the%20Opposition%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20said%20some%20powers%20are%20trying%20to%20weaken%20national%20unity%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20politics%20and%20called%20upon%20people%20to%20identify%20and%20fight%20against%20this%20%26quot%3Balliance%20of%20urban%20Naxals%26quot%3B.%C2%A0The%20Prime%20Minister%20was%20speaking%20on%20National%20Unity%20Day%2C%20which%20coincided%20with%20Diwali%20this%20time%2C%20near%20Sardar%20Vallabhbhai%20Patel's%20grand%20statue%20at%20Kewadiya%20in%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCountries%20are%20growing%20apart%2C%20but%20coming%20close%20to%20India.%20This%20is%20not%20ordinary%2C%20a%20new%20history%20is%20being%20written.%20The%20world%20is%20watching%20how%20India%20is%20resolving%20its%20issues.%20So%20we%20have%20to%20protect%20our%20unity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20after%20paying%20tributes%20to%20Sardar%20Patel%2C%20who%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20national%20integration%20after%20India's%20Independence%20in%201947.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20perverted%20powers%20are%20worried%20about%20India's%20rise.%20Within%20India%2C%20and%20outside%20it%2C%20such%20people%20are%20trying%20to%20create%20instability%20and%20anarchy.%20They%20want%20the%20wrong%20message%20to%20go%20to%20global%20investors.%20These%20people%20are%20targeting%20the%20forces%2C%20running%20misinformation%20campaigns.%20They%20are%20trying%20to%20divide%20(people)%20in%20the%20name%20of%20caste.%20They%20aim%20to%20weaken%20India's%20society%20and%20unity.%20They%20don't%20want%20India%20to%20be%20developed%20because%20the%20politics%20of%20'poor%20India%2C%20weak%20India'%20suits%20them.%20So%20they%20are%20breaking%20India%20in%20the%20name%20of%20the%20Constitution.%20We%20have%20to%20identify%20this%20alliance%20of%20Urban%20Naxals%20and%20fight%20against%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20did%20not%20explicitly%20name%20any%20Opposition%20party%20or%20leader%2C%20the%20reference%20was%20clear.%20The%20INDIA%20Opposition%20bloc%2C%20led%20by%20the%20Congress%2C%20built%20its%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20campaign%20around%20a%20'save%20Constitution'%20slogan%20and%20is%20demanding%20a%20caste%20Census%20to%20ensure%20better%20representation%20of%20backward%20classes%20in%20jobs%20and%20education.%20In%20this%20general%20election%2C%20the%20BJP%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20returned%20to%20power%20despite%20falling%20short%20of%20getting%20a%20majority%20on%20its%20own.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20paid%20tribute%20to%20Sardar%20Patel%20and%20said%20the%C2%A0BJP%20government's%20vision%20reflects%20its%20commitment%20to%20national%20unity.%20He%20said%20a%20'one%20nation%2C%20one%20tax'%20system%20and%20abolished%20the%20Article%20370%20wall%2C%20revoking%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20special%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20discriminatory%20policies%20and%20intent%20of%20previous%20governments%20weakened%20national%20unity.%20Over%20the%20past%2010%20years%2C%20the%20new%20governance%20model%20has%20eliminated%20discrimination.%20We%20have%20chosen%20the%20path%20of%20sabka%20saath%20sabka%20vikas.%20This%20approach%20has%20ended%20the%20dissatisfaction%20among%20people%20and%20enhanced%20their%20trust%20in%20development%20schemes%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20Aadhaar%2C%20which%20represents%20'one%20nation%2C%20one%20identity'%2C%20is%20being%20discussed%20globally.%20%26quot%3BWe%20brought%20'one%20nation%2C%20one%20tax'%20system%20through%20GST.%20We%20brought%20'one%20nation%2C%20one%20health%20insurance'%20scheme%20through%20Ayushman%20Bharat.%20Now%2C%20we%20are%20working%20towards%20'one%20nation%2C%20one%20election'%20that%20will%20strengthen%20democracy%20and%20optimise%20resources.%20India%20is%20also%20moving%20towards%20'one%20nation%2C%20one%20civil%20code'.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20country%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20happy%20that%20after%2070%20years%20of%20Independence%2C%20a%20'one%20nation%2C%20one%20Constitution'%20pledge%20has%20been%20fulfilled.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20my%20biggest%20tribute%20to%20Sardar%20sahab.%20For%2070%20years%2C%20Baba%20Saheb%20Ambedkar's%20Constitution%20was%20not%20implemented%20across%20the%20country.%20Those%20who%20chant%20the%20name%20of%20the%20Constitution%20insulted%20it%20so%20much.%20The%20reason%20was%20the%20wall%20of%20Article%20370%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20Article%20370%20has%20been%20buried%20forever.%20For%20the%20first%20time%2C%20voting%20was%20done%20without%20discrimination%20in%20this%20Assembly%20election.%20For%20the%20first%20time%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20there%20has%20taken%20oath%20on%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India.%20This%20scene%20must%20have%20given%20immense%20satisfaction%20to%20the%20makers%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%2C%20their%20souls%20must%20have%20found%20peace%20and%20this%20is%20our%20humble%20tribute%20to%20the%20makers%20of%20the%20Constitution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20this%20National%20Unity%20Day%20marks%20the%20beginning%20of%20Sardar%20Patel's%20150th%20birth%20anniversary%20and%20the%20country%20will%20celebrate%20this%20occasion%20for%20two%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnity%20is%20important%20for%20economic%20progress%20and%20our%20goal%20to%20become%20a%20developed%20nation.%20This%20unity%20is%20important%20for%20social%20harmony.%20If%20we%20are%20committed%20to%20social%20justice%2C%20unity%20is%20the%20pre-condition.%20Let%20us%20move%20forward%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730359860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fv98g9u78_pm-modi_625x300_31_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fconstitution-was-not-implemented-across-india-for-70-years-we-demolished-article-370-wall-pm-modi-on-national-unity-day-6912721%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BConstitution%20was%20not%20implemented%20across%20India%20for%2070%20years%2C%20we%20demolished%20Article%20370%20wall%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20Modi%20on%20National%20Unity%20Day%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fconstitution-was-not-implemented-across-india-for-70-years-we-demolished-article-370-wall-pm-modi-on-national-unity-day-6912721%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IPL%20Retention%20Live%3A%20KKR%20To%20End%2010-Year%20Partnership%20With%20Overseas%20Star%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIPL%202025%20Retention%20Live%20Updates%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20As%20per%20a%20report%2C%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20are%20likely%20to%20part%20ways%20with%20Andre%20Russell%2C%20a%20star%20all-rounder%20that%20has%20been%20with%20them%20for%20the%20past%2010%20seasons%20of%20Indian%20Premier%20League.%20Russell%20made%20his%20IPL%20debut%20playing%20for%20KKR%20back%20in%202014.%20He%20has%20remained%20part%20of%20all%20the%20IPL%20editions%20since%20then%2C%20barring%202017.%20The%20D%20Day%20is%20finally%20here%20as%20the%20retentions%20for%20the%20upcoming%20edition%20of%20the%20IPL%20will%20be%20announced.%205%20PM%20is%20the%20deadline%20for%20all%20the%20franchises%20to%20submit%20their%20list%20of%20retentions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20the%20Live%20Updates%20of%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%202025%20Retentions%20Announcement%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%22%2C%22published%22%