rlet%20Witch%2C%20reached%20the%20end%20of%20the%20Witches%E2%80%99%20Road%20in%20the%20two-part%20finale%20of%20%E2%80%9CAgatha%20All%20Along%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20it%20very%20little%20was%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Adam%20B.%20Vary%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fagatha-all-along-finale-explained-billy-tommy-witches-road-nicholas-scratch-1236195942%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Harshit%20Rana%20Added%20To%20Squad%20For%203rd%20NZ%20Test%3F%20India%20Assistant%20Coach%20Says...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20have%20not%20added%20any%20extra%20player%20to%20their%20squad%20ahead%20of%20the%20third%20Test%20against%20New%20Zealand%20and%20also%20does%20not%20have%20any%20plans%20of%20resting%20pace%20spearhead%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20before%20the%20upcoming%20long%20five-Test%20series%20against%20Australia%20Down%20Under%20starting%20in%20November.%20Amid%20reports%20that%20the%20team%20management%20had%20called%20up%20Harshit%20Rana%20to%20train%20and%20bowl%20for%20the%20team%20ahead%20of%20the%20third%20Test%20against%20New%20Zealand%20at%20the%20Wankhede%20Stadium%2C%20there%20was%20expectation%20that%20Rana%20could%20be%20added%20to%20the%20squad%20just%20like%20Washington%20Sundar%20was%20called%20up%20just%20before%20the%20second%20Test%20in%20Pune%20as%20the%20Delhi%20medium%20pacer%20is%20one%20of%20the%20bowlers%20picked%20in%20the%20Australia%20tour%20squad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20India's%20assistant%20coach%20Abhishek%20Nayar%20clarified%20that%20not%20extra%20player%20has%20been%20added%20to%20squad%20while%20also%20confirming%20that%20they%20have%20no%20plans%20of%20resting%20Bumrah%20despite%20it%20being%20an%20inconsequential%20Test%20as%20New%20Zealand%20has%20already%20taken%20an%20unassailable%202-0%20lead%20in%20the%20three-match%20series.%20There%20has%20been%20concerns%20regarding%20the%20workload%20of%20Indian%20pacers%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%20as%20many%20of%20them%20have%20broken%20down%20even%20during%20a%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBumrah%20has%20a%20history%20with%20injuries%20and%20thus%20there%20was%20hope%20that%20the%20team%20management%20would%20like%20to%20keep%20him%20fresh%20ahead%20of%20the%20Australia%20series.%20But%20Nayar%20said%20the%20team%20management%20is%20aware%20of%20his%20workload%20but%20feels%20that%20the%20seasoned%20pacer%20from%20Gujarat%20has%20not%20bowled%20too%20many%20overs%20in%20two%20Tests%2C%20which%20incidently%20ended%20prematurely%2C%20thus%20giving%20him%20some%20extra%20rest%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20in%20the%20two%20Test%20matches%20he's%20(Bumrah)%20bowled%20around%2020%2C%2025%20overs.%20So%20he's%20not%20bowled%20a%20lot.%20Yes%2C%20there'll%20always%20be%20a%20thought%20process%20about%20his%20workload.%20Also%2C%20we%20played%20two%20games%20where%20we%20not%20at%205k%20cricket%2C%20it's%20been%20more%20three%2C%20three-and-a-half%20days%2C%20so%20he%20could%20have%20rest.%20But%20Booms%20is%20very%20important%20to%20us%20and%20the%20workload%20will%20always%20be%20something%20on%20our%20mind%2C%26quot%3B%20Nayar%20said%20in%20a%20pre-match%20press%20conference%20at%20the%20wankhede%20Stadium%20here%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20reason%20for%20the%20team%20management%20opting%20against%20resting%20Bumrah%20is%20that%20the%20Wankhede%20pitch%20is%20expected%20to%20help%20seamers%20in%20the%20first%20hour%20or%20so%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20always%20believe%20that%20Wankhede%20will%20always%20give%20pace%20a%20chance%20no%20matter%20what%2C%20especially%20when%20Mumbai%20winter%20doesn't%20feel%20like%20it.%20But%20in%20the%20morning%20there%20will%20be%20a%20bit%20of%20moisture%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20bit%20of%20dew%20around.%20So%20you%20will%20expect%20the%20first%20sessions%20to%20have%20a%20bit%20of%20swing.%20I'm%20not%20sure%20of%20the%20pitche%20yet%20because%20it's%20covered%2C%20but%20if%20the%20pitch%20is%20hard%2C%20then%20there%20will%20be%20a%20bit%20of%20swing%20as%20well.%20But%20at%20Wankhede%2C%20you%20will%20always%20see%20fast%20bowlers%20with%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20smile%20on%20their%20face%20in%20the%20morning%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Nayar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20Indian%20team%20needs%20do%20some%20self-reflection%20after%20losing%20a%20home%20series%20in%20more%20than%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirstly%2C%20I%20will%20start%20with%20giving%20a%20lot%20of%20credit%20to%20New%20Zealand%20for%20the%20way%20they%20played%20and%20countered%20spin%20in%20the%20two%20Test%20matches.%20I%20feel%20that%20though%20the%20conditions%20will%20be%20different%20with%20a%20red-soil%20pitch.%20The%20last%20time%20we%20played%20on%20a%20red%20soil%2C%20which%20was%20in%20Chennai%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20guys%20have%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20local%20cricketers%20and%20they%20understand%20what%20these%20conditions%20are%20and%20how%20the%20pitch%20is%20going%20to%20pan%20out.%20I%20think%20it's%20more%20about%2C%20at%20this%20level%2C%20self%20reflection%20for%20every%20player%20to%20go%20in%20and%20understand%20their%20game%20plans%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20for%20us%2C%20it's%20more%20about%20self%20reflection%20and%20what%20we%20can%20do%20as%20a%20team.%20There's%20always%20advantages%2C%20but%20I%20always%20believe%20that%20what%20you've%20done%20in%20the%20past%20doesn't%20really%20matter%20in%20the%20present.%20It's%20about%20how%20you%20turn%20up%20on%20that%20particular%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730357280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Ftuup79k_ha