o%20ask%20how%20I%20should%20be%20addressing%20them%20when%20they%20get%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Moore%20shared%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirror.co.uk%2F3am%2Fus-celebrity-news%2Fhow-meghan-markle-must-addressed-33997418%5C%22%3EThe%20Mirror%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20advice%20he%20received%20was%3A%20a%20simple%20%E2%80%9CMa'am%E2%80%9D%20for%20Meghan%20and%20%E2%80%9CSir%E2%80%9D%20for%20Prince%20Harry.%20This%20guideline%20differs%20from%20the%20formal%20address%20typically%20reserved%20for%20royals%2C%20where%20they%20are%20addressed%20first%20as%20%E2%80%9CYour%20Royal%20Highness%E2%80%9D%20followed%20by%20%E2%80%9CMa'am%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9CSir.%E2%80%9D%20However%2C%20after%20stepping%20back%20from%20royal%20duties%20in%202020%2C%20the%20Duke%20and%20Duchess%20of%20Sussex%20no%20longer%20hold%20%E2%80%9CHRH%E2%80%9D%20titles%2C%20making%20this%20protocol%20unnecessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20choice%20to%20maintain%20formal%20titles%20is%20different%20from%20Prince%20Harry's%20previous%20stance%20on%20informality.%20In%202020%2C%20he%20attended%20a%20tourism%20conference%20in%20Edinburgh%2C%20where%20he%20told%20the%20host%20and%20the%20audience%20to%20simply%20call%20him%20%E2%80%9CHarry.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Invictus%20Games%20is%20an%20international%20multi-sport%20event%20for%20wounded%2C%20injured%20and%20sick%20servicemen%20and%20women%2C%20both%20active%20and%20veteran.%20The%20Games%20were%20founded%20by%20Prince%20Harry%20in%202014%2C%20inspired%20by%20the%20Warrior%20Games%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20ex-royal%20couple's%20February%20trip%20to%20Vancouver%2C%20the%20Sussexes%20took%20time%20to%20connect%20with%20the%20Invictus%20community%20on%20Valentine's%20Day%2C%20joining%20participants%20for%20winter%20sports%20training.%20This%20event%2C%20named%20the%20%E2%80%9COne%20Year%20to%20Go%E2%80%9D%20celebration%2C%20spanned%20three%20days%20and%20allowed%20members%20of%20the%20international%20Invictus%20community%20to%20participate%20in%20various%20winter%20sports%20in%20preparation%20for%20next%20year's%20games.%20The%20Vancouver%20event%2C%20which%20will%20take%20place%20from%20February%208%20to%20February%2016%2C%202025%2C%20will%20build%20on%20the%20success%20of%20the%202023%20games%20held%20in%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20last%20year's%20games%2C%20Meghan%20Markle%20hinted%20at%20the%20possibility%20of%20bringing%20along%20their%20children%2C%20Prince%20Archie%20and%20Princess%20Lilibet.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730355960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Ffv3rifoc_meghan-markle_625x300_01_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Finvictus-games-ceo-reveals-how-meghan-markle-is-to-be-addressed-6912815%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Meghan%20Markle%20insists%20on%20being%20addressed%20as%20%26quot%3BMa'am%2C%26quot%3B%20Invictus%20Games%20CEO%20Scott%20Moore%20has%20revealed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Finvictus-games-ceo-reveals-how-meghan-markle-is-to-be-addressed-6912815%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHorrible%20Scene%26quot%3B%3A%20Suspected%20Gang's%20Wild%20Bash%20Leaves%20Airbnb%20In%20Ruins%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20homeowner%20in%20a%20Colorado%20mountain%20town%20found%20her%20Airbnb%20rental%20in%20ruins%20after%20a%20chaotic%20party%20allegedly%20hosted%20by%20members%20of%20the%20Tren%20de%20Aragua%20gang.%20Karen%20Martiz%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20property%20in%20Evergreen%20%E2%80%94%20around%2048%20km%20west%20of%20Denver%20%E2%80%94%20reported%20damages%20amounting%20to%20%2416%2C000%20(around%20Rs%2013.45%20lakh).%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20wild%20bash%2C%20Ms%20Martiz%20found%20a%20scene%20of%20utter%20disarray%2C%20with%20cigarette%20butts%20scattered%20about%2C%20chewing%20gum%20smeared%20across%20carpets%2C%20walls%20and%20ceilings%2C%20and%20hundreds%20of%20empty%20alcohol%20bottles%20alongside%20drug%20paraphernalia.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMs%20Martiz%20is%20convinced%20the%20mess%20was%20the%20result%20of%20the%20Venezuelan%20prison%20gang's%20activities.%20The%20local%20law%20enforcement%20agency%2C%20the%20Clear%20Creek%20County%20Sheriff's%20Office%2C%20supports%20this%20claim%2C%20saying%20they%20suspected%20members%20of%20Tren%20de%20Aragua%20were%20part%20of%20the%20large%20group%20of%2080%20to%20100%20individuals%20who%20partied%20at%20the%20Airbnb.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%9CI%20have%20put%20all%20my%20energy%20and%20love%20into%20this%20property%20to%20make%20it%20beautiful%20for%20my%20guests.%20It's%20a%20beautiful%20place.%20Everybody%20loved%20it.%20We%20have%20been%20hosting%20for%20two%20years%20and%20this%20was%20the%20first%20time%20that%20I%20showed%20up%20here%20and%20my%20house%20was%20completely%20destroyed.%20I%20couldn't%20believe%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ms%20Martiz%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fcolorado-airbnb-host-faces-16k-damages-after-suspected-migrant-gang-members-destroy-property%5C%22%3EFox%20News%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMartiz%20described%20entering%20her%20home%20after%20the%20guests'%20departure%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Chorrible%20scene%2C%E2%80%9D%20expressing%20disbelief%20over%20the%20level%20of%20destruction.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20walked%20into%20my%20house%2C%20I%20couldn't%20believe%20I%20was%20actually%20living%20this.%20Because%20until%20you%20live%20it%2C%20you%20are%20like%2C%20%E2%80%98Is%20this%20even%20something%20that%20could%20happen%20to%20people%3F'%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Tren%20de%20Aragua%20gang's%20activities%20have%20been%20reported%20across%20states%2C%20including%20Aurora%2C%20Colorado%2C%20where%20they%20have%20taken%20control%20of%20multiple%20apartment%20complexes%20and%20committed%20violent%20crimes%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F09%2F12%2Fus-news%2Finside-the-migrant-gang-warzone-of-aurora-colorado%2F%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%9CIt's%20very%20real%2C%20and%20this%20group%20of%20people%20(Tren%20de%20Aragua)%20are%20doing%20it%20to%20people%20like%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ms%20Martiz%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20New%20York%20Post%20has%2C%20in%20the%20past%2C%20reported%20on%20the%20Tren%20de%20Aragua%20gang's%20infiltration%20into%20the%20Denver%20suburb%2C%20detailing%20how%20the%20gang%20took%20over%20multiple%20neglected%20apartment%20complexes%2C%20with%20their%20regional%20leader%2C%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98Cookie%2C'%20implicated%20in%20violent%20crimes.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20problem%20garnered%20national%20attention%2C%20notably%20from%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20who%20visited%20Aurora%20earlier%20in%20October%20for%20a%20rally.%20He%20announced%20his%20intention%20to%20invoke%20a%20226-year-old%20law%20aimed%20at%20dismantling%20Tren%20de%20Aragua%20and%20deporting%20its%20members.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnTrump%20told%20supporters%20at%20the%20rally%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20will%20rescue%20Aurora%20and%20every%20town%20that%20has%20been%20invaded%20and%20conquered%2C%E2%80%9D%20emphasising%20his%20administration's%20commitment%20to%20either%20imprisoning%20or%20expelling%20these%20%E2%80%9Cvicious%20and%20bloodthirsty%20criminals.%E2%80%9D%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMs%20Martiz%20agrees%20with%20Trump's%20assessment%20of%20the%20gang's%20menace%20to%20society.%20%E2%80%9CAbsolutely%20no%20exaggeration%20at%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CThese%20people%20are%20not%20here%20to%20do%20good.%20They%20have%20nothing%20to%20lose.%20They%20don't%20care.%20They're%20just%20coming%20in%2C%