0due%20to%20bad%20weather.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20paid%20tributes%20to%20Sardar%20Patel%20for%20his%20key%20role%20in%20unifying%20over%20560%20princely%20states%20after%20India's%20Independence%20in%201947.%20%26quot%3BThis%20statue%20'Desh%20Ka%20Vallabh'%20will%20inspire%20people%20reminding%20them%20of%20the%20strength%20in%20unity%20and%20the%20unwavering%20spirit%20required%20to%20build%20a%20nation%20as%20diverse%20as%20ours%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20paid%20respects%20to%20Major%20Bob%20Khathing%20for%20his%20contribution%20to%20the%20Northeast%20region%20and%20national%20security.%20%26quot%3BMajor%20Khathing%20not%20only%20led%20the%20peaceful%20integration%20of%20Tawang%20into%20India%20but%20also%20established%20essential%20military%20and%20security%20frameworks%2C%20including%20the%20Sashastra%20Seema%20Bal%2C%20Nagaland%20Armed%20Police%2C%20and%20the%20Naga%20Regiment.%20The%20'Museum%20of%20Valour'%20now%20stands%20as%20a%20tribute%20to%20his%20bravery%20and%20foresight%2C%20inspiring%20generations%20to%20come%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20step%20towards%20easing%20the%20tension%20at%20the%20LAC%20following%20the%20violent%20clashes%20in%20Galwan%20Valley%20in%202020%2C%20India%20and%20China%20last%20week%20agreed%20on%20a%20patrolling%20agreement%20under%20which%20both%20sides%20will%20fall%20back%20to%20their%20pre-April%202020%20positions.%20Delhi%20and%20Beijing%2C%20however%2C%20will%20continue%20to%20have%20surveillance%20options%20in%20Depsang%20and%20Demchok%2C%20and%20will%20inform%20the%20other%20side%20before%20stepping%20out%20on%20patrol%20%26quot%3Bto%20avoid%20any%20miscommunication%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agreement%20was%20announced%20hours%20before%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20Russia%20visit%20for%20the%20BRICS%20summit%20where%20he%20spoke%20to%20China%20President%20Xi%20Jinping.%20Mr%20Modi%20told%20the%20Chinese%20leader%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20