ction%20with%20North%20Korea%20does%20not%20violate%20international%20law.%20Russia%20has%20not%20denied%20the%20involvement%20of%20North%20Korean%20troops%20in%20the%20war%2C%20which%20it%20has%20been%20waging%20in%20Ukraine%20since%20February%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20if%20everything%20that's%20being%20said%20about%20the%20cooperation%20between%20Russia%20and%20North%20Korea%20by%20our%20Western%20colleagues%20is%20true%2C%20why%20is%20it%20that%20the%20United%20States%20and%20allies%20are%20trying%20to%20impose%20on%20everyone%20the%20flawed%20logic%20that%20they%20have%20the%20right%20to%20help%20the%20Zelenskiy%20regime%20...%20and%20Russian%20allies%20have%20no%20right%20to%20do%20a%20similar%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20Nebenzia%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20U.N.%20Ambassador%20Sergiy%20Kyslytsya%20responded%3A%20%26quot%3BNone%20of%20the%20countries%20that%20provide%20assistance%20to%20Ukraine%20is%20under%20Security%20Council%20sanctions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReceiving%20assistance%20from%20the%20fully-sanctioned%20North%20Korea%20is%20a%20brazen%20violation%20of%20the%20U.N.%20Charter%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BSending%20the%20DPRK%20troops%20to%20support%20Russia's%20war%20of%20aggression%20against%20Ukraine%20is%20a%20flagrant%20violation%20of%20international%20law.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENorth%20Korea%20has%20been%20under%20U.N.%20Security%20Council%20sanctions%20since%202006%20and%20the%20measures%20have%20been%20steadily%20strengthened%20over%20the%20years%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20halting%20Pyongyang's%20development%20of%20nuclear%20weapons%20and%20ballistic%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENorth%20Korea%20has%20not%20acknowledged%20the%20deployment%20of%20troops%20to%20Russia%2C%20but%20said%20any%20such%20move%20would%20be%20compliance%20with%20international%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Russia's%20sovereignty%20and%20security%20interests%20are%20exposed%20to%20and%20threatened%20by%20continued%20dangerous%20attempts%20of%20the%20United%20States%20and%20the%20West%2C%20and%20if%20it%20is%20judged%20that%20we%20should%20respond%20to%20them%20with%20something%2C%20we%20will%20make%20a%20necessary%20decision%2C%26quot%3B%20North%20Korea's%20U.N.%20Ambassador%20Song%20Kim%20told%20the%20council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPyongyang%20and%20Moscow%20maintain%20close%20contact%20with%20each%20other%20on%20mutual%20security%20and%20development%20of%20the%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20deputy%20U.S.%20Ambassador%20Robert%20Woodward%20warned%20North%20Korean%20leader%20Kim%20Jong%20Un%3A%20%26quot%3BShould%20DPRK's%20troops%20enter%20Ukraine%20in%20support%20of%20Russia%2C%20they%20will%20surely%20return%20in%20body%20bags.%20So%20I%20would%20advise%20Chairman%20Kim%20to%20think%20twice%20about%20engaging%20in%20such%20reckless%20and%20dangerous%20behavior.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730350860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F8i3lk79_russias-un-ambassador-vassily-nebenzia-_625x300_31_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fif-west-aids-ukraine-why-cant-north-korea-help-us-russia-asks-at-un-6911796%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Russia's%20envoy%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20on%20Wednesday%20questioned%20why%20its%20allies%20like%20North%20Korea%20could%20not%20help%20Moscow%20in%20its%20war%20against%20Ukraine%20given%20Western%20countries%20claim%20the%20right%20to%20help%20Kyiv.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fif-west-aids-ukraine-why-cant-north-korea-help-us-russia-asks-at-un-6911796%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2210%20Delhi%20Spots%20That%20Saw%20Most%20Road%20Accidents%20In%202023%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPedestrians%20continue%20to%20be%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20in%20road%20crashes%20in%20Delhi%2C%20accounting%20for%2043%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20victims%2C%20followed%20by%20two-wheelers%2C%20according%20to%20Delhi%20Road%20Crash%20Fatalities%20Report%202023.%20The%20number%20of%20deaths%20in%20road%20crashes%20decreased%20by%200.55%20per%20cent%20from%201%2C264%20in%202022%20to%201%2C257%20in%202023%20in%20spite%20of%20an%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20vehicles%20registered%20on%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20also%20been%20an%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20prosecutions%20from%204%2C38%2C052%20in%202022%20to%206%2C39%2C097%20in%202023%2C%20along%20with%20other%20corrective%20measures%20taken%20by%20the%20traffic%20unit%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20released%20on%20Wednesday%20by%20Delhi%20Police%20Commissioner%20Sanjay%20Arora%20contains%20an%20analysis%20of%20the%20accidents%20that%20occurred%20last%20year%20along%20with%20the%20causes%2C%20patterns%20and%20suggestions%20in%20road%20design%2C%20regulation%20and%20prosecution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20will%20help%20the%20police%20outline%20a%20road%20safety%20action%20plan%20that%20will%20involve%20the%20joint%20efforts%20of%20multiple%20departments%20to%20improve%20education%2C%20engineering%2C%20enforcement%2C%20and%20emergency%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20focus%20is%20on%20designing%20a%20forgiving%20infrastructure%20to%20reduce%20the%20chances%20of%20crashes%20and%20then%20reducing%20the%20fatalities%20in%20the%20cases%20where%20they%20do%20occur%2C%20a%20senior%20police%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20efforts%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Traffic%20Police%20have%20led%20to%20a%20reduction%20in%20road%20crash%20deaths%20in%20Delhi%20by%2020%20per%20cent%20over%20the%20last%20decade.%20Continuing%20our%20endeavour%20to%20save%20lives%2C%20we%20have%20now%20increased%20focus%20on%20more%20pedestrian-centric%20traffic%20management%2C%26quot%3B%20Special%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(Traffic)%2C%20Ajay%20Chaudhary%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20report%20has%20identified%20pedestrians%20as%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20road%20users%20followed%20by%20two-wheeler%20riders%20constituting%2043%20per%20cent%20and%2038%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total%20fatalities%20in%20road%20crashes%2C%20respectively%2C%20in%202023%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chaudhary%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoad%20crashes%20not%20only%20affect%20the%20livelihoods%20of%20the%20persons%20involved%20but%20also%20leave%20a%20longer%20imprint%20on%20the%20victims'%20families.%20It%20often%20pushes%20people%20to%20the%20brink%20of%20poverty%20and%20costs%20the%20economy%20heavily%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20focus%20areas%20of%20Delhi%20Traffic%20Police%20have%20been%20to%20enhance%20the%20use%20of%20technology%20in%20smooth%20traffic%20management%20and%20surveillance%20and%20to%20improve%20road%20infrastructure%2C%20particularly%20in%20design%20and%20standards%2C%20for%20the%20vulnerable%20categories%20of%20road%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20pedestrians%2C%20cyclists%20and%20motorcyclists%20are%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20road%20users%2C%20the%20focus%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20on%20road%20safety%20measures%2C%20including%20prosecutions%20and%20awareness%20campaigns%20on%20the%20use%20of%20helmets%2C%20zebra%20crossings%2C%20subways%2C%20encroachment-free%20safe%20pedestrian%20walkways%2Ffootpaths%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Traffic%20Police%20has%20also%20recommended%20design%20interventions%20at%20crash-prone%20locations%20to%20reduce%20fatalities%2C%20Mr%20Chaudhary%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20Delhi%20Traffic%20Police%20identified%2010%20such%20black%20spots%20--%20ISBT%20Kashmere%20Gate%2C%20Mukarba%20Chowk%2C%20Libaspur%20bus%20stand%2C%20Kashmere%20Gate%20Chowk%2C%20Burari%20Chowk%2C%20Britannia%20Chowk%2C%20Bhalswa%20Chowk%2C%20Wazirpur%20Depot%2C%20Mori%20Gate%20round%20about%20and%20Gandhi%20Vihar%20bus%20stand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20these%2C%2010%20other%20roads%20in%20Delhi%20recorded%2010%20or%20more%20deaths%20in%202023%2C%20including%20NH-8%2C%20Road%20No.%2056%2C%20Kanjhawala%20Road%2C%20NH-24%2C%20Road%20No.%20201%2C%20Patel%20Road%2C%20Pankha%20Road%2C%20Vikas%20Marg%20and%20Narela%20Road%2C%20Mr%20Chaudhary%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730350560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fo0mjhfq_delhi-road-crash_625x300_31_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-road-crash-fatalities-report-2023-10-delhi-spots-that-saw-most-road-accidents-in-2023-6913013%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20number%20of%20deaths%20in%20road%20crashes%20decreased%20by%200.55%20per%20cent%20from%201%2C264%20in%202022%20to%201%2C257%20in%202023%20in%20spite%20of%20an%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20vehicles%20registered%20on%20the%20road.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-road-crash-fatalities-report-2023-10-delhi-spots-that-saw-most-road-accidents-in-2023-6913013%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Suicide%20pact%3A%20Sick%20mom%2C%20single%20daughter%20hang%20to%20death%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730349935000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114804580%2Cimgsize-21424.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fvijayawada%2Fsuicide-pact-sick-mom-single-daughter-hang-to-death-in-andhra-pradesh%2Farticleshow%2F114804494.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20Kakinada%20district%2C%20an%20elderly%20woman%2C%20Akasam%20Saraswathi%2C%20and%20her%20daughter%20Swati%20ended%20their%20lives.%20Saraswathi%20had%20severe%20health%20issues%2C%20and%20Swati%2C%20devoted%20to%20her%20care%2C%20stayed%20single.%20Police%20found%20Saraswathi's%20body%20on%20a%20bed%20and%20Swati%20hanging%20from%20a%20ceiling%20fan.%20A%20case%20is%20under%20investigation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22SAMSON%20RAJ%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fvijayawada%2Fsuicide-pact-sick-mom-single-daughter-hang-to-death-in-andhra-pradesh%2Farticleshow%2F114804494.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIf%20They%20Want%20To...%26quot%3B%3A%20New%20Hezbollah%20Chief%20Says%20Open%20To%20Truce%20With%20Israel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHezbollah's%20new%20leader%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20the%20beleaguered%20Lebanese%20movement%20could%20agree%20to%20a%20ceasefire%20under%20certain%20terms%2C%20as%20Israeli%20forces%20expand%20their%20bombardment%20of%20the%20group's%20bastions.%20Naim%20Qassem's%20statement%20came%20as%20Israel's%20security%20cabinet%20met%20to%20discuss%20a%20possible%20truce%2C%20but%20also%20as%20Israel%20attacked%20the%20eastern%20Lebanese%20city%20of%20Baalbek%20and%20said%20it%20had%20killed%20another%20senior%20Hezbollah%20commander.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELebanon's%20premier%20Najib%20Mikati%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bcautiously%20optimistic%26quot%3B%20about%20a%20ceasefire%20in%20%26quot%3Bthe%20coming%20hours%20or%20days%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20broadcaster%20Al-Jadeed%2C%20Mikati%20said%20US%20envoy%20Amos%20Hochstein%20had%20suggested%20%26quot%3Bthat%20perhaps%20we%20could%20reach%20a%20ceasefire%20in%20the%20coming%20days%2C%20before%20the%20fifth%26quot%3B%20of%20November%2C%20when%20the%20US%20election%20takes%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQassem%20became%20leader%20of%20the%20Iran-backed%20armed%20movement%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20following%20the%20assassination%20of%20his%20predecessor%20Hassan%20Nasrallah%20by%20Israel%20in%20a%20massive%20air%20strike%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20first%20speech%20since%20taking%20over%2C%20he%20said%20Hezbollah%20could%20continue%20to%20resist%20Israeli%20air%20and%20ground%20attacks%20in%20Lebanon%20for%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20also%20opened%20the%20door%20to%20a%20negotiated%20truce%2C%20if%20presented%20with%20an%20Israeli%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20Israelis%20decide%20that%20they%20want%20to%20stop%20the%20aggression%2C%20we%20say%20we%20accept%2C%20but%20under%20the%20conditions%20that%20we%20see%20as%20appropriate%20and%20suitable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQassem%20however%20added%20that%20Hezbollah%20had%20not%20yet%20received%20a%20credible%20proposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Energy%20Minister%20Eli%20Cohen%20said%20the%20country's%20security%20cabinet%20was%20meeting%20to%20discuss%20what%20terms%20it%20might%20offer%20to%20secure%20a%20truce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20discussions%2C%20I%20think%20it%20will%20still%20take%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Cohen%2C%20a%20former%20intelligence%20minister%2C%20told%20Israeli%20public%20radio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Israel's%20Channel%2012%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20met%20ministers%20late%20Tuesday%20to%20discuss%20Israel's%20demands%20in%20return%20for%20a%2060-day%20truce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20include%20that%20Hezbollah%20withdraw%20north%20of%20the%20Litani%20River%2C%20some%2030%20kilometres%20(20%20miles)%20from%20the%20Israeli%20frontier%2C%20and%20that%20the%20Lebanese%20state's%20army%20deploy%20along%20the%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Act%20forcefully'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20international%20intervention%20mechanism%20would%20be%20established%20to%20enforce%20the%20truce%2C%20but%20Israel%20would%20demand%20a%20guarantee%20that%20it%20maintain%20freedom%20of%20action%20in%20case%20of%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20State%20Department%20said%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20Middle%20East%20adviser%20Brett%20McGurk%20and%20Hochstein%20were%20headed%20to%20Israel%20Wednesday%20to%20seek%20progress%20on%20deals%20to%20end%20both%20the%20Gaza%20and%20Lebanon%20wars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20%26quot%3Bare%20travelling%20to%20Israel%20to%20engage%20on%20issues%20including%20a%20diplomatic%20resolution%20in%20Lebanon%2C%20as%20well%20as%20how%20we%20get%20to%20an%20end%20to%20the%20conflict%20in%20Gaza%2C%26quot%3B%20State%20Department%20spokesman%20Matthew%20Miller%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20ground%2C%20explosions%20rocked%20Lebanon's%20eastern%20city%20of%20Baalbek%20shortly%20after%20Israel's%20military%20warned%20residents%20it%20would%20%26quot%3Bact%20forcefully%20against%20Hezbollah%20interests%20within%20your%20city%20and%20villages%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELebanon's%20health%20ministry%20said%20at%20least%2019%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20Israeli%20strikes%20on%20two%20areas%20in%20the%20Baalbek%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20said%20it%20struck%20Hezbollah%20%26quot%3Bcommand%20and%20control%20centres%20and%20terrorist%20infrastructure%26quot%3B%20in%20areas%20of%20Baalbek%20and%20Nabatiyeh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20Lebanon's%20health%20ministry%20said%2011%20people%20were%20killed%20and%2015%20wounded%20in%20Israeli%20strikes%20on%20the%20town%20of%20Sohmor%20in%20the%20eastern%20Bekaa%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHezbollah%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20said%20it%20had%20fired%20rockets%20and%20drones%20at%20three%20military%20positions%20in%20northern%20Israel%2C%20including%20near%20Haifa%20and%20Acre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20later%20said%20it%20fired%20rockets%20at%20a%20military%20training%20camp%20southeast%20of%20Tel%20Aviv.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20in%20Lebanon%20began%20late%20last%20month%2C%20nearly%20a%20year%20after%20Hezbollah%20began%20low-intensity%20cross-border%20fire%20into%20Israel%20in%20support%20of%20Hamas%20following%20its%20October%207%2C%202023%20attack%20on%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20has%20killed%20at%20least%201%2C754%20people%20in%20Lebanon%20since%20September%2023%2C%20according%20to%20an%20AFP%20tally%20of%20health%20ministry%20figures%2C%20although%20the%20real%20number%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20military%20says%20it%20has%20lost%2037%20soldiers%20in%20Lebanon%20since%20ground%20operations%20began%20on%20September%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EShort%20term%20truce%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Gaza%2C%20there%20were%20more%20deadly%20strikes%20Wednesday%20as%20international%20mediators%20prepared%20to%20propose%20a%20short-term%20truce%20to%20free%20hostages%20and%20avert%20a%20humanitarian%20catastrophe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENews%20of%20a%20potential%20breakthrough%20in%20truce%20talks%20came%20a%20day%20after%20an%20Israeli%20strike%20on%20a%20single%20Gaza%20residential%20block%20killed%20nearly%20100%20people%20and%20triggered%20international%20revulsion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%2C%20Qatari%20and%20Egyptian%20mediators%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20negotiate%20a%20truce%20for%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20Mossad%20spy%20chief%20David%20Barnea%2C%20CIA%20director%20Bill%20Burns%20and%20Qatari%20Prime%20Minister%20Mohammed%20bin%20Abdulrahman%20bin%20Jassim%20Al-Thani%20held%20their%20latest%20round%20of%20secretive%20talks%20on%20Sunday%20and%20Monday%20in%20Doha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20a%20source%20close%20to%20the%20talks%20told%20AFP%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20that%20the%20senior%20officials%20discussed%20proposing%20a%20%26quot%3Bshort-term%26quot%3B%20truce%20of%20%26quot%3Bless%20than%20a%20month%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposal%20would%20include%20the%20exchange%20of%20Israeli%20hostages%20for%20Palestinians%20in%20Israeli%20prisons%2C%20and%20an%20increase%20in%20aid%20to%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUS%20officials%20believe%20that%20if%20a%20short-term%20deal%20can%20be%20reached%2C%20it%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20more%20permanent%20agreement%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Hamas%20official%20said%20the%20group%20would%20discuss%20any%20ideas%20for%20a%20Gaza%20ceasefire%20that%20included%20an%20Israeli%20withdrawal%2C%20but%20had%20not%20officially%20received%20any%20comprehensive%20proposals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Israeli%20Defence%20Minister%20Yoav%20Gallant%20told%20troops%20to%20continue%20exerting%20pressure%20%26quot%3Bin%20order%20to%20create%20the%20conditions%20necessary%20to%20ensure%20the%20return%20of%20the%20hostages%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETuesday's%20strike%20in%20the%20northern%20Gaza%20district%20of%20Beit%20Lahia%20collapsed%20a%20building%20and%20left%20at%20least%2093%20dead%2C%20including%20many%20children%2C%20according%20to%20the%20territory's%20civil%20defence%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUN%20chief%20Antonio%20Guterres%20was%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20shocked%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20strike%2C%20his%20spokesman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20State%20Department%20spokesman%20Miller%20meanwhile%20said%20Israel%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20doing%20enough%20to%20get%20us%20the%20answers%20that%20we%20have%20requested%26quot%3B%20over%20the%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas's%20October%207%2C%202023%20attack%20resulted%20in%201%2C206%20deaths%2C%20mostly%20civilians%2C%20according%20to%20an%20AFP%20tally%20of%20official%20Israeli%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20response%20has%20led%20to%20the%20deaths%20of%2043%2C163%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%2C%20most%20of%20them%20civilians%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Hamas-run%20territory's%20health%20ministry%2C%20figures%20which%20the%20United%20Nations%20consider%20reliable.