ng%2C%20reconnecting%20with%20friends%20and%20family%2C%20and%20reigniting%20lost%20connections.%20He%20changed%20his%20phone%20number%20and%20effectively%20switched%20off%20from%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20his%20biggest%20learnings%2C%20he%20says%2C%20was%20breaking%20free%20from%20the%20societal%20definitions%20of%20masculinity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20story%20reflects%20the%20conditioning%20of%20masculinity%20that%20many%20boys%20in%20our%20country%20experience.%20Everything%20is%20linked%20to%20money%20and%20providing.%20We%20never%20take%20time%20to%20find%20joy%20in%20life.%20Historically%2C%20men%20have%20been%20viewed%20as%20providers%20and%20women%20are%20seen%20as%20nurturers.%20Today%2C%20while%20women%20play%20both%20roles%2C%20men%20are%20still%20not%20encouraged%20to%20embrace%20their%20nurturing%20side.%20We%20need%20to%20understand%20the%20burden%20of%20patriarchy%20on%20men%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20expresses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENikhil%20wanted%20to%20break%20out%20of%20the%20cycle%20where%20one%20looks%20at%20happiness%20as%20a%20destination.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20need%20to%20recognise%20your%20worth%20as%20a%20human%20being.%20You%20owe%20it%20to%20yourself%20to%20celebrate%20yourself%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20how%2C%20as%20children%2C%20our%20parents%20promised%20to%20buy%20us%20video%20games%20or%20new%20phones%20or%20toys%20if%20we%20scored%20well%20in%20exams%2C%20Nikhil%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20carry%20this%20conditioning%20as%20adults%2C%20leading%20to%20rewarding%20ourselves%20on%20every%20academic%20or%20professional%20achievement.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherapy%20helped%20the%20Mumbai%20resident%20unlearn%20and%20understand%20himself%20on%20a%20deeper%20level.%20During%20his%20eight-month%20break%2C%20Nikhil%20sought%20to%20find%20purpose%20in%20life.%20He%20loved%20teaching%20and%20interacting%20with%20young%20people%2C%20while%20his%20skills%20lay%20in%20entertainment%20and%20writing.%20How%20could%20he%20combine%20the%20two%20to%20create%20a%20tangible%20impact%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20youngsters%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pursuit%20to%20answer%20this%20question%20led%20to%20the%20launch%20of%20Yuvaa%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYuvaa%20is%20a%20purpose-driven%20youth%20media%2C%20research%2C%20and%20impact%20organisation%20that%20hopes%20to%20start%20meaningful%20conversations%20among%20India%E2%80%99s%20youth%2C%20particularly%20Gen%20Z.%20We%20want%20to%20listen%20to%20young%20people%20in%20schools%20and%20colleges%20who%20are%20feeling%20lonely%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENikhil%20began%20with%20a%20roadshow%2C%20travelling%20to%20150%20campuses%20in%2035%20cities%20over%20nine%20months.%20The%20idea%2C%20he%20says%2C%20was%20to%20talk%20about%20mental%20health%20and%20sexual%20health%2C%20providing%20a%20safe%20space%20for%20young%20people%20to%20share%20their%20stories.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20this%20roadshow%2C%20Nikhil%20encountered%20many%20young%20boys%20whose%20stories%20moved%20him%20deeply.%20%E2%80%9CAn%2018-year-old%20boy%20told%20me%20that%20no%20one%20had%20ever%20told%20him%20%E2%80%98I%20love%20you.%E2%80%99%20Another%20teen%20shared%20that%20no%20one%20had%20ever%20hugged%20him.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20give%20intimacy%20to%20our%20boys%20and%20tell%20them%20it%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332810%2Fkota-suicides-iit-jee-neet-coaching-classes-entrance-exams-students%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eokay%20to%20express%20themselves%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20wanted%20to%20provide%20a%20space%20to%20all%20the%20boys%20and%20girls%20in%20our%20country%20by%20creating%20communities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20achie