%20our%20responsibility%20to%20provide%20complete%20quality%20healthcare%20and%20not%20simply%20fund%20the%20activity.%20L%26amp%3BT%20ensures%20services%20are%20provided%20by%20experienced%20doctors%20and%20multi-disciplinary%20health%20professionals.%20This%20ensures%20the%20sustainability%20of%20the%20drive.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20out%20how%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20community%20have%20been%20the%20barometer%20for%20new%20specialities%20being%20added%2C%20she%20says%20the%20current%20module%20boasts%20a%20plethora%20of%20services%2C%20ensuring%20that%20patients%20get%20comprehensive%20care%20under%20one%20roof.%20These%20include%20consultations%20for%20reproductive%20health%2C%20orthopaedic%20concerns%2C%20dental%20concerns%2C%20gynaecological%20conditions%2C%20respiratory%20concerns%2C%20skin%20and%20venereal%20diseases%2C%20ENT%20concerns%2C%20testing%2C%20treatment%20and%20counselling%20for%20tuberculosis%20and%20mental%20health%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20commitment%20to%20pioneer%20community%20health%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecognising%20that%20it%20is%20a%20privilege%20to%20be%20of%20service%20to%20those%20in%20the%20greatest%20need%2C%20Larsen%20%26amp%3B%20Toubro%20%E2%80%94%20a%20technology-led%20multinational%20that%20provides%20engineering%2C%20construction%2C%20manufacturing%2C%20and%20financial%20services%20%E2%80%94%20incepted%20the%20idea%20of%20community%20health%20centres.%20Today%2C%20these%20are%20staffed%20by%20expert%20doctors%2C%20nurses%2C%20and%20paramedics%20%E2%80%94%20keen%20on%20paying%20their%20dues%20back%20to%20society%20through%20their%20service.%20The%20therapeutic%20modalities%20are%20backed%20by%20excellent%20diagnostics%20and%20the%20latest%20technology%2C%20including%20X-rays%2C%20ultrasound%2C%20dental%20equipment%2C%20and%20equipment%20deployed%20in%20scopies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Madhuri%20Franklin%2C%20who%20is%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20the%20operations