ng%20individuals%20face%20profound%20physical%20or%20emotional%20challenges%20that%20make%20conventional%20workspaces%20daunting.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20our%20Bengaluru%20centre%2C%20we%20operate%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F351436%2Fhow-to-start-organic-farming-techies-switching-to-farming-roja-reddy-nanda-kishore-in-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20organic%20store%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhere%20the%20youth%20can%20earn%20a%20living.%20This%20space%20not%20only%20provides%20them%20with%20a%20safe%20environment%20but%20also%20allows%20them%20to%20engage%20in%20meaningful%20activities%20during%20the%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ramya%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReflecting%20on%20her%20journey%2C%20she%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20often%20think%20those%20in%20the%20social%20sector%20are%20here%20to%20give%2C%20but%20the%20reality%20is%20that%20we%20gain%20far%20more%20than%20we%20give.%20This%20work%20deepens%20our%20understanding%20of%20ourselves%20%E2%80%94%20as%20human%20beings%2C%20as%20parents%2C%20as%20mentors%20%E2%80%94%20and%20expands%20our%20capacity%20for%20empathy.%20Our%20entire%20team%20has%20grown%20alongside%20the%20youth%20we%20serve.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20ahead%2C%20Ramya%20expresses%20her%20aspirations%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20hope%20to%20eventually%20extend%20our%20efforts%20to%20children%20in%20conflict%20with%20the%20law%20(CCLs).%20We%E2%80%99ve%20had%20some%20initial%20engagements%2C%20but%20we%20recognise%20the%20unique%20challenges%20involved.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20vast%20area%2C%20and%20while%20we%E2%80%99re%20not%20quite%20there%20yet%2C%20we%20aim%20to%20develop%20a%20programme%20that%20supports%20CCLs%20in%20securing%20employment%20and%20managing%20their%20lives%20independently.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20what%20message%20she%20would%20give%20to%20youth%20considering%20the%20programme%2C%20Ramya%20shares%2C%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20p